  'Start your reply with { and end with }.',
  '',
  styleNote,
  '',
  '═══════════════════════════════════════════',
  'MANDATORY 10-SECTION FLOW — IN THIS EXACT ORDER',
  '═══════════════════════════════════════════',
  'Total slide budget for this session: ' + slideTarget + ' slides. Distribute roughly:',
  '  1. Title + Icebreaker / Rapport          (2 slides)   types: title, body',
  '  2. Warm-up — activate prior knowledge    (2-3 slides) types: body, fact, fill-blank',
  '  3. Learning Objective                     (1 slide)    type:  objectives',
  '  4. Definition — core concept             (2-3 slides) types: section, definition, body',
  '  5. Explanation + Examples                 (6-10 slides) types: definition, examples, compare, fact, mnemonic',
